pytest is python based testing framework
write and execute test code 
detect test file and test function automatically 
pip - package installer for python (it will install or uninstall packages related to python )
python version - 
pip install pytest 
test case has to start with test* 
Assertions and different syntaxes
selenium with python
markers - @mark.skip , with conditions ,multiple markers , pytest - m "not smoke" ,  pytest - m "not product or smoke" , pytest - m "not product and smoke" 
 
fixtures - before and after each test cases - avoid repetitiion , which are common for all cases 

